      • TimeBasedRetentionPolicy

        public TimeBasedRetentionPolicy(Config config)
        Creates a new TimeBasedRetentionPolicy using RETENTION_TIMEBASED_DURATION_KEY in the config
          Some Example values for RETENTION_TIMEBASED_DURATION_KEY are
        • P20D = 20 Days
        • P20H = 20 Hours
        • P2Y = 2 Years
        • P2Y3M = 2 Years and 3 Months
        • PT23M = 23 Minutes (Note this is different from P23M which is 23 Months)
        Parameters:
        config - that holds retention duration in ISO8061 format at key RETENTION_TIMEBASED_DURATION_KEY.
